
### 3. `package.json`

This file is created with `npm init` and defines project metadata and dependencies.

```json
{
  "name": "product-management-system",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A simple product management API",
  "main": "server.js",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "node server.js",
    "dev": "nodemon server.js"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "express": "^4.18.2",
    "pg": "^8.7.1",
    "body-parser": "^1.19.1",
    "cors": "^2.8.5",
    "dotenv": "^10.0.0"
  }
}
